data.description: So many updates with this 3 bedrooom, 1 1/2 bath home that sits on .54 acres!!!  Let's first start with the newly updated mudroom with new walls and floors!  Off of the mudroom, you'll have a newly updated half bathroom on one side and a new open pantry on the other side!  As you migrate through the spacious eat-in kitchen, you will enter the living room with new carpet and natural light!  There is new carpet throughout the upstairs and downstairs.  As you enter the 2nd floor, you'll have a bedroom that has new walls and floors!  Then the icing on the cake is the newly updated full bathroom.  The goodies extend the the exterior of the house!  Newer roof on the front and in the process of the back part of the roof being replaced and new gutters being installed.  Last but not least the 24x24 detached garage, the 24x36 pole constructed building and the chicken coop all ready for you to make your own!  Both detached garage and pole constructed building are insulated with a wood burning stove in the 24x36 building.  Take a look today!
